quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  107,1,"Mbega warabonye uwuhakana yivuye inyuma, izuka ry’ibiremwa n’impera yavyo ku musi w’izuka?"
  107,2,"Uyo, ni uwuryagumba agahahaza impfuvyi, agahonyanga agateka kayo ku karenganyo;"
  107,3,"Ntanahimirize gufungurira abakene, nkeswe kubafungurira we nyene."
  107,4,"Burya guhanwa nya guhanwa, ni ukw’abasenga mu buryarya;"
  107,5,"Abirengagiza amasengesho yabo mu kutayasengera ku mwanya wayo no mu kutubahiriza ibisabwa vyayo;"
  107,6,"Abiyerekana mu vyo bakora kugira bashimwe n’abantu;"
  107,7,"Bakanimana mu kudatizanya utumaramuziro."
